query:
INSERT INTO iot_data_points (device_id, tag_name, tag_type, value, quality, timestamp) 
SELECT id, 'temperature', 'analog', '25.40', 'good', NOW() FROM iot_devices WHERE device_code = 'TEMP-001'
UNION ALL
SELECT id, 'pressure', 'analog', '1013.25', 'good', NOW() FROM iot_devices WHERE device_code = 'PRESS-002'
UNION ALL
SELECT id, 'vibration', 'analog', '2.80', 'uncertain', NOW() FROM iot_devices WHERE device_code = 'VIB-003'
UNION ALL
SELECT id, 'power', 'analog', '0.00', 'bad', NOW() FROM iot_devices WHERE device_code = 'PWR-004';
